"Parris Island" often brings to mind a very specific kind of hardship, but for those seeking broader horizons, the name also redirects to the less harrowing, more varied collection of entries found at [Parris Island (disambiguation)](/Parris_Island_(disambiguation)). One might also note that "Paris Island" – a common, if misguided, phonetic approximation – is distinct from the rather more romantic and significantly less muddy [Island of Paris](/Island_of_Paris), a geographical entity that rarely involves drill instructors or the smell of sweat and fear.

